@* صفحة تأكيد الحجز - بتظهر بعد ما المريض يبعت الحجز *@
@model Maw3dyCare.Models.Maw3dyCareDB.Reservations
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Reservation Confirmed";
}

<style>
    /* body {
        background-color: #f0f4ff;
    } */

    body {
        background: var(--bg-main);
    }

    @* الكارد الرئيسي *@
    .confirm-wrapper {
        max-width: 420px;
        margin: 60px auto;
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 36px 32px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.10);
        text-align: center;
        border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    }

    @* رقم الحجز *@
    .reservation-badge {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe, #00c6ff);
        color: white;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 14px 32px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 12px 0 20px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    @* رسالة التأكيد *@
    .confirm-msg {
        background-color: var(--badge-bg);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    @* أسهم التنقل *@
    .nav-arrows {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .arrow-btn {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 6px 14px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
        background: var(--bg-card);
        transition: all .15s;
    }

        .arrow-btn:hover {
            background: var(--badge-bg);
            color: var(--text-main);
        }
</style>

<div class="container">
    <div class="confirm-wrapper">

        @* ===== أسهم التنقل ===== *@
        @* السهم الأيسر = رجوع لصفحة الحجز | الأيمن = الذهاب لمتابعة الحالة *@
        <div class="nav-arrows">
            <a href="/Maw3dyCare/Reserve/@Model.HospitalId" class="arrow-btn">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Back
            </a>
            <a href="/Maw3dyCare/Status/@Model.ReservationId" class="arrow-btn">
                Track Status <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

        @* ===== عنوان ===== *@
        <p class="text-muted small mb-1">Reservation Number</p>

        @* ===== رقم الحجز = نوع السرير + رقم الـ Reservation ===== *@
        <div class="reservation-badge">
            @Model.BedTypes.Name-@Model.ReservationId.ToString("D2")
        </div>

        @* ===== اسم المستشفى ===== *@
        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">
            <i class="bi bi-hospital text-primary"></i> @Model.Hospitals.Name
        </p>

        @* ===== رسالة الـ 30 دقيقة ===== *@
        <div class="confirm-msg">
            <p class="fw-semibold mb-1" style="color:#b07d2e;">
                Your bed is reserved for 30 minutes.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                Please arrive at the hospital within this time.
            </p>
        </div>

        @* ===== زرار متابعة الحالة ===== *@
        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
            <a href="/Maw3dyCare/Status/@Model.ReservationId"
               class="btn btn-primary rounded-3">
                <i class="bi bi-satellite-dish"></i> Track My Reservation
            </a>
            <a href="/Maw3dyCare/Hospitals"
               class="btn btn-outline-secondary rounded-3">
                <i class="bi bi-house"></i> Back to Hospitals
            </a>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>